  "subject": "Refer to SDN-R as controller persona",
  "commit_message": "Refer to SDN-R as controller persona\n\nUpdated SDN-R user documentation to refer to SDN-R as a 'SDN controller\npersona for Radio' rather than 'SDN controller for Radio'.  This\nis to clarify that SDN-R is a controller persona (i.e. a\ndeployment configuration), and not a competing, independent\ncontroller to SDN-C.\n\nChange-Id: I8fd6f790e70a59c1c73bb80b8fc0914fd7d1b634\nIssue-ID: CCSDK-1809\nSigned-off-by: Dan Timoney <dtimoney@att.com>\n",
